   * :attr:	:xmlattr:`PostOfflineDelay`
     :val:	0...2\ :sup:`32`\  - 1
     :def:	0 sec
     :desc:	Additional delay to change quality marking of station's DI/AI objects if station hasn't been online for a very long time.
		Quality marking of station's DI/AI objects will be changed after configured number of seconds following status change to OFFLINE.
		(Application example: DI/AI objects can be marked with Not Topical [:lemonobgtext:`NT`] bit when station status changes to OFFLINE i.e. after :include-arg:`1` timer expires and Invalid [:lemonobgtext:`IV`] bit after this delay expires.)

